<div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_whole_program_compiler">Whole Program Compiler</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>Each of these techniques requires whole-program analysis</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>But, additional benefits:</p>
<div class="ulist">
<ul>
<li>
<p>eliminate (some) variability in programming styles</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>specialize representations</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>simplifies and improves runtime system</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</li>
</ul>
